The '''1904 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their fourteenth ever season of organized football. The Keydets held a 3-5 record in [[William Roper (American football)|William Roper]]'s 2nd and last season as VMI head coach.<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
